message.text:
🎮🐉🎲𝘙𝘦𝘢𝘥𝘺 𝘵𝘰 𝘳𝘰𝘭𝘭 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘥𝘪𝘤𝘦 𝘰𝘯 𝘢 𝘣𝘳𝘢𝘯𝘥-𝘯𝘦𝘸 𝘺𝘦𝘢𝘳?⭐

During the 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐧𝐲, FEU Tech SAGE unveiled our 𝐀𝐕𝐏 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒.𝐘. 𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟓–𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟔!✨

Whether it’s game development, tabletop quests, casual matches, or epic campaigns, you’ll find a home right here in 𝐒𝐀𝐆𝐄. ⚔️👾

Here’s to a year filled with games, stories, and camaraderie. 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐲! 🕹️🦦💙

#FITSAGE2526
#SAGE2526
#PassionIntoProgress
#JoinSAGE

🎬 Director: Allen Alwin David
🎨 Co-director, VA, Assets: Arianna Salumbides
🎞️ Editor: John Leland Miñon
📝 Caption: Ina Bautista

🎵 Music: It’s Going Down Now — Lotus Juice & Azumi Takahashi, composed by Atsushi Kitajoh

message.text:
🎮🐉🎲𝘙𝘦𝘢𝘥𝘺 𝘵𝘰 𝘳𝘰𝘭𝘭 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘥𝘪𝘤𝘦 𝘰𝘯 𝘢 𝘣𝘳𝘢𝘯𝘥-𝘯𝘦𝘸 𝘺𝘦𝘢𝘳?⭐

During the 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐧𝐲, FEU Tech SAGE unveiled our 𝐀𝐕𝐏 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒.𝐘. 𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟓–𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟔!✨

Whether it’s game development, tabletop quests, casual matches, or epic campaigns, you’ll find a home right here in 𝐒𝐀𝐆𝐄. ⚔️👾

Here’s to a year filled with games, stories, and camaraderie. 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐲! 🕹️🦦💙

#FITSAGE2526
#SAGE2526
#PassionIntoProgress
#JoinSAGE

🎬 Director: Allen Alwin David
🎨 Co-director, VA, Assets: Arianna Salumbides
🎞️ Editor: John Leland Miñon
📝 Caption: Ina Bautista

🎵 Music: It’s Going Down Now — Lotus Juice & Azumi Takahashi, composed by Atsushi Kitajoh

🎮🐉🎲𝘙𝘦𝘢𝘥𝘺 𝘵𝘰 𝘳𝘰𝘭𝘭 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘥𝘪𝘤𝘦 𝘰𝘯 𝘢 𝘣𝘳𝘢𝘯𝘥-𝘯𝘦𝘸 𝘺𝘦𝘢𝘳?⭐

During the 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐧𝐲, FEU Tech SAGE unveiled our 𝐀𝐕𝐏 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒.𝐘. 𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟓–𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟔!✨

Whether it’s game development, tabletop quests, casual matches, or epic campaigns, you’ll find a home right here in 𝐒𝐀𝐆𝐄. ⚔️👾

Here’s to a year filled with games, stories, and camaraderie. 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐲! 🕹️🦦💙

#FITSAGE2526
#SAGE2526
#PassionIntoProgress
#JoinSAGE

🎬 Director: Allen Alwin David
🎨 Co-director, VA, Assets: Arianna Salumbides
🎞️ Editor: John Leland Miñon
📝 Caption: Ina Bautista

🎵 Music: It’s Going Down Now — Lotus Juice & Azumi Takahashi, composed by Atsushi Kitajoh
